# -Branch A in Yangon city
female_member = 80
female_normal = 81
male_member = 87
male_normal = 91

x = np.arange(2)
width = 0.35

fig, ax = plt.subplots()

rects1 = ax.bar(x, [female_member, male_member], width, label='Member', color='#439981')
rects2 = ax.bar(x + width, [female_normal, male_normal], width, label='Normal', color='#78b19f')

ax.set_xticks(x + width / 2)
ax.set_xticklabels(['Female', 'Male'])
ax.legend()

plt.show()
